{"tid":1827521,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"華為新年致辭：2019 年收入保持增長　但增長幅度未達預期","createTime":"2020-01-17T04:20:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-17T04:29:31.000Z","uid":66087,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6c2dbb749d24b4802ab3342ea2259869cfcb70a7","tid":1827521,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T04:20:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://chinese.engadget.com/chinese-2019-12-31-huawei-failed-to-meet-2019-growth-goal.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchinese.engadget.com%2Fchinese-2019-12-31-huawei-failed-to-meet-2019-growth-goal.html&d=yrakYkBpMe8E3VCHF0kcyhD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=bf098426\" target=\"_blank\">https://chinese.engadget.com/chinese-2019-12-31-huawei-failed-to-meet-2019-growth-goal.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190217/photo/bkn-20190217093159897-0217_00952_001_01p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190217%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190217093159897-0217_00952_001_01p.jpg&h=f90d83ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n華為董事長徐直軍發布新年致辭，指出2019年預計全年實現銷售收入超過8500億人民幣，按年增長達18%，雖然沒有達到年初預期，但公司整體經營穩健，經受住考驗。<br />\n<br />\n其中，智能手機業務保持穩健增長，發貨量超過2.4億台。<br />\n<br />\n徐直軍表示，2020年華為要全力打造華為作業系統（Huawei Mobile Services，HMS）生態，支持智能手機在海外銷售，同時2020年要把鯤鵬與昇騰處理器作為重要的增長方向。"},{"pid":"6c8bfbb7e8a4a0a58636a0c6e980423dcd441d10","tid":1827521,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T04:21:41.000Z","msg":"支出呢"},{"pid":"3cd65c94ea1c846075cfb9d8d22c128984fa6580","tid":1827521,"uid":313615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T04:29:31.000Z","msg":"<strong>華為251事件<br />\n華為妳仲冇同李洪元 曾夢say sorry，抵死</strong>"}]}